title: Kentucky's Largest Vaccine Site Preparing To Open
cleaned_text:
Officials say it will take a minimum of 100 volunteers a day to keep the site's 28 lanes moving.

The site will be able to administer 4,000 vaccines a day when it officially opens on Monday.
